==English==
===Intransitive verb===
'''to stutter'''

# to speak with involuntary disruption or blocking of speech (as by spasmodic repetition or prolongation of vocal sounds)
# to move or act in a halting or spasmodic manner
#:''The old jalopy bucks and stutters uphill.''

====Synonyms====
*(1): [[stammer]]
*(2): [[judder]]

=== Noun ===
# an act or instance of stuttering
# a speech disorder involving stuttering accompanied by fear and anxiety

